org.eclipse.debug.core.commands

Interface IEnabledStateRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDebugCommandRequest, IRequest

    public interface IEnabledStateRequest
extends IDebugCommandRequest
    A request to update the enabled state of a command. A enabled state request is passed to a IDebugCommandHandler to update the enabled state of the handler.

    Clients than invoke command handlers may implement this interface.

    Since:
    3.3
